NAME
     Poll

PARAMETERS
     None

DESCRIPTION
     Loads the selected mailer program and polls your boss node. The exact
poll command is taken from the network associated with the current area.

RESULT CODES
     None

NOTES
     None
---
NAME
     firstarea

PARAMETERS
     None

DESCRIPTION
     Jumps to the first message area.

RESULT CODES
     None

NOTES
     Areas are numbered in the order they are scanned when Cyclone starts
up. You cannot rely on any particular area having the same number next time
you jump to it as deleting or creating areas causes area tag numbers to
change.
---
NAME
     firstmessage

PARAMETERS
     None

DESCRIPTION
     Moves to message #1.

RESULT CODES
     None

NOTES
     None
