@node "version" "Version Info"
@next "Author"
@prev "MUI"
* v1.25c 28/03/97 ==============

New Stuff

 + Aliases
 + Re-nameable areas
 + In-line FTX code interpreter.
 + New quote system and message display engine.
 + User configurable area list ordering
 + Edit header function
 + Enhanced e-mail support
 + Two-pass dupe checker with selectable buffer size (2k - 128k)
 + Mail Shunt module can now shunt on addresses
 + Improved quoting
 + Async polling
 + Optional vertical bars in area & message lists
 + Drop-to-post AppIcon
 + Purge All function added
 + More ARexx scripts
 + Export command can now export just one network rather than all
 + Confirmation requester on quit function
 + Inbound packet & file backup

Fixed Bugs

 + Auto-created areas now use correct network addresses
 + FLO file overwrite problem fixed
 + Message List delete button now works for multiple messages
 + Stack problems with some editors and tag generators fixed
 + Enforcer hits with some ARexx commands removed
 + Duplicate keyboard shotcuts re-done
 + Fixed parsing problems with 3D addresses


* v1.21a 10/01/97 =======================

New Features and Improvements:

 + E-Mail Gateway Support
 + New X flag for unreplied messages
 + Improved keyboard shortcuts
 + Faster area list window, with new area name sort routine
 + Right cursor on last message pops up area list
 + Return key skips to next area


Eradicated Bugs:

 + Lock-up when replying to messages containing very long UU-Encoded
   files fixed.
 + Minor problems with some converted Spot netmail areas fixed.


* v1.20a 01/01/97 =======================

 @{u}First iteration of the 1.2x code base.@{uu}

 NEW

 + ARexx menu
 + Vertical toolbar option
 + Virtual toolbar option
 + Mail shunting / Message re-direction
 + Flexible filtering in message list
 + Configurable highlighting in message & area lists
 + Pop-Up menus
 + Quick validation & re-index mode
 + Multiple tagline files
 + Copy to clipboard option
 + Import-time packet backup option
 + Import-time file backup option
 + Inteligent bad packet detection
 + Spot message base converter
 + Debug mode
 + Tooltypes
 + Extra control codes (|T & |F)
 + All-new file request handler
 + Help bubbles


 CHANGED

 + Area searcher can now search body text
 + All list replaced with Fast Search list
 + Improved thread list
 + Improved user list
 + Fastimport now scans Origin line if MSGID kludge unavailable
 + Eliminated the 'missing space' quote problem

@endnode

